The paper deals with a computer vision problem of colorizing anime line art, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques such as Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) and WGAN-GP, which are commonly used in the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of local features network, which is related to the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper deals with the problem of generalization, which is related to the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of creating high-quality illustrations, which is related to the sub-category of graphics (cs.GR).
